# Input

```grit
`$method('$message')` where {
  if ($message <: r"Hello, .*!") {
    $method => `console.info`
  } else {
    $method => `console.warn`
  }
}

```


# Formatted

```grit
`$method('$message')` where {
	if ($message <: r"Hello, .*!") { $method => `console.info` } else {
		$method => `console.warn`
	}
}

```
